name: Chief Chirpa
Lore: 'Leader of Wicket''s Ewok tribe for 42 seasons. Head of the Council of Elders. Decided to spare Han''s Rebels and join their fight against the Empire.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Endor. Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one non-unique Ewok to same Endor site from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
